      "content": "therapy doesn't change the fact that i'm a drain on them. i've lived a long life, i've done my part... i just don't see the point in lingering on and making their lives harder. it feels almost selfish to keep going when i know my being here just makes everything more complicated for my kids. do you think there's any nobility in just... letting go? to make things easier for the people i love?",
